This repository provide demo codes and data of the modeling pipeline for patient-specific prediction of breast cancer response to neoadjuvant therapy. 
The framework is illustrated in the document, "codestructure".


Please refers to this paper for more details on the methodology and associated image processing pipeline:

Angela M. Jarrett, Anum S. Kazerouni, Chengyue Wu, John Virostko, Anna G. Sorace, Julie C. DiCarlo, David A. Hormuth, II,
David A. Ekrut, Debra Patt, Boone Goodgame, Sarah Avery, Thomas E. Yankeelov. Quantitative magnetic resonance imaging and tumor
forecasting of breast cancer patients in the community setting. Nature Propotol, 2021 (in press).

Further questions and discussion are welcome through the repository, or via email (ajarrett@utexas.edu, cw35926@utexas.edu).
